import React from "react"

export default function Meme(){
    return(
        <main>
            <form className="form">
                <input type="text"
                    placeholder="Top text"
                    className="form-input"
                    />
                <input type="text"
                    placeholder="Bottom text"
                    className="form-input"
                />
                <button className="form--button">GET IT</button>
            </form>
        </main>
    )
}
